title: Ep 51: MOM-trepreneurs Wanted
description:
Today's proceedings:  Facebook drama ensues after a babysitter finds a new job, a guy got more then he bargained for during his proposal , we read some stories from a new subreddit "Does Anyone Else?", and we find a man who loves using multiple alarms to wake up.  And for this week's Circle Jurdge we read about a cute/cringe post from "girlfriend of the pod" and see what the internet had to say about it.
